&nbsp;
I got to know that&nbsp;the count for unread emails will be different for both Outlook client and OWA as this completely depends on how many emails you read from your OWA and Outlook client. There is a difference in how it gets processed between the two. It does not sync the way it syncs your incoming or outgoing emails.
